name: Pixelidolia - Morning Glory
description:
Pixelidolia is a pixel artwork project of mine that I combined with a double-vision painting style. Merger of two words, "pixel"and "pareidolia". Influenced by double-vision painting style artists such as Octavio Ocampo and Oleg Suphliak.

This time the theme is a tribute to Japanese City Pop icons, Tatsuro Yamashita and Mariya Takeuchi. Combined with pixel illustration influenced by Hiroshi Nagai's style.
